{"_path":"/tags/os/centos","_dir":"os","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"CentOS","description":"CentOS (Community ENTerprise Operating System) 是一个免费的、开源的操作系统，它是基于 Red Hat Enterprise Linux (RHEL) 的源代码构建的。CentOS 提供了 RHEL 的许多特性和稳定性，但不包括商业支持，使其成为许多企业和开发者的首选。","name":"centos","icon":"logos:centos-icon","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"centos"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CentOS"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"icon","props":{"className":["size-32"],"name":"logos:centos"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CentOS (Community ENTerprise Operating System) 是一个免费的、开源的操作系统，它是基于 Red Hat Enterprise Linux (RHEL) 的源代码构建的。CentOS 提供了 RHEL 的许多特性和稳定性，但不包括商业支持，使其成为许多企业和开发者的首选。以下是对 CentOS 的详细介绍，包括其关键特点、历史演变和主要版本。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"关键特点"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"关键特点"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"源自 RHEL"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：CentOS 基于 RHEL 的源代码构建，因此具有与 RHEL 相同的稳定性和兼容性。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"免费和开源"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：CentOS 是完全免费的，任何人都可以下载、使用和修改其源代码。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"长生命周期"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：每个 CentOS 版本都有一个长达 10 年的支持周期，提供长期的安全更新和维护。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"稳定性"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：适用于服务器和企业环境，提供高可靠性和稳定性。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"软件兼容性"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：与 RHEL 兼容的二进制文件，使得在 RHEL 上开发的软件可以无缝运行在 CentOS 上。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"广泛的社区支持"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：拥有一个活跃的用户和开发者社区，提供丰富的资源和帮助。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"历史演变"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"历史演变"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"起源和早期发展"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"起源和早期发展"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2004"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：CentOS 项目由 Gregory Kurtzer 启动，首个版本 CentOS 3.1 基于 RHEL 3 源代码发布。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2006"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：CentOS 4 发布，基于 RHEL 4，进一步巩固了其在企业服务器市场的地位。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"重要里程碑"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"重要里程碑"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2007"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：CentOS 5 发布，基于 RHEL 5，增强了虚拟化支持和安全特性。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2011"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：CentOS 6 发布，基于 RHEL 6，引入了更强大的性能和稳定性改进。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2014"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：CentOS 项目与 Red Hat 合作，成为 Red Hat 的官方社区版。CentOS 7 发布，基于 RHEL 7，引入了 systemd、XFS 文件系统等新特性。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"最新版本"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"最新版本"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2019"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：CentOS 8 发布，基于 RHEL 8，包含新的应用流 (AppStream) 存储库，改进了容器支持和性能。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2020"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：宣布 CentOS 8 将在 2021 年底结束支持，并引入 CentOS Stream 作为未来的开发模式，提供一个滚动更新的发布版本，定位于 RHEL 的上游开发版本。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"主要版本"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"主要版本"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CentOS 3"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：最早的 CentOS 版本，基于 RHEL 3。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CentOS 4"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：引入了 SELinux 和更好的硬件支持。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CentOS 5"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：增强了虚拟化和安全特性。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CentOS 6"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：引入了新的功能和性能改进，支持更长的生命周期。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CentOS 7"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：大幅更新，包括 systemd、XFS 文件系统和 Docker 支持。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CentOS 8"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：最新的稳定版本，提供了最新的技术和改进。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CentOS Stream"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：一个滚动更新的版本，位于 Fedora 和 RHEL 之间，作为 RHEL 的上游开发版本。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"主要功能和组件"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"主要功能和组件"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"YUM 包管理器"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：用于安装、更新和管理软件包。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"systemd"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：系统和服务管理器，取代了传统的 init 系统。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"SELinux"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：强制访问控制安全系统，增强了系统安全性。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"KVM 和 QEMU"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：用于虚拟化支持，提供高性能的虚拟机管理。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"XFS 文件系统"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：默认文件系统，提供高性能和可扩展性。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Docker 和 Podman"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：容器技术支持，简化了应用部署和管理。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"总结"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"总结"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CentOS 是一个功能强大、稳定且免费的操作系统，广泛应用于服务器和企业环境。通过基于 RHEL 源代码构建，CentOS 提供了与 RHEL 相同的稳定性和兼容性，但没有商业支持，使其成为许多预算有限的企业和开发者的理想选择。随着 CentOS Stream 的引入，CentOS 项目继续在开源社区中发挥重要作用，推动 Linux 生态系统的发展和创新。"}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":5,"depth":5,"links":[{"id":"centos","depth":2,"text":"CentOS","children":[{"id":"关键特点","depth":3,"text":"关键特点"},{"id":"历史演变","depth":3,"text":"历史演变","children":[{"id":"起源和早期发展","depth":4,"text":"起源和早期发展"},{"id":"重要里程碑","depth":4,"text":"重要里程碑"},{"id":"最新版本","depth":4,"text":"最新版本"}]},{"id":"主要版本","depth":3,"text":"主要版本"},{"id":"主要功能和组件"